<p>political index: <%= @follow_cost2.political_index.round(2) %></p>
<!--p>followers 2 weeks ago: <%= @tc2.followers_2w_ago %></p-->  
<p>followers yesterday: <%= @tc2.followers_yesterday %></p>  
